any graphics or photos you feed into the tool."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"legal-section","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Log Files"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"BGCleaner follows a standard procedure of using log files. These files log visitors when they visit websites. All hosting companies do this as part of hosting services' analytics. The information collected by log files includes internet protocol (IP) addresses, browser type, Internet Service Provider (ISP), date and time stamp, referring/exit pages, and possibly the number of clicks. These are not linked to any information that is personally identifiable. The purpose of the info is for analyzing trends, administering the site, tracking users' movement on the website, and gathering demographic information."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"legal-section","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Cookies and Web Beacons"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Like any other website, BGCleaner uses \"cookies\". These cookies are used to store information including visitors' preferences, and the pages on the website that the visitor accessed or visited. The information is used to optimize the users' experience by customizing our web page content based on visitors' browser type and/or other information."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"legal-section","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Google DoubleClick DART Cookie"}],["$","p",null,{"children":["Google is one of the third-party vendors on our site. It also uses cookies, known as DART cookies, to serve ads to our site visitors based upon their visit to www.website.com and other sites on the internet. However, visitors may choose to decline the use of DART cookies by visiting the Google ad and content network Privacy Policy at the following URL: ",["$","a",null,{"href":"https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer","children":"https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads"}]]}]]}],"$L5","$L6","